Type = Graphic, Audio, Font - One of these options are available.
Scope = 1 - Resource is required on all layouts. For example, the font and audio files.
Scope = 2,3,4 ... - Used only inside a group of layouts. For example, the graphics files.

Resource - Graphic
Image = Resource/Test.png - The path to the image, should be valid or else will be removed from process.

Resource - Font
Font = Resource/Font.ttf - The path to the font, should be valid or else will be removed from process.
-->

